rComments: Come to class and take some notes. If not, then you won't make it. Great teacher. Knows his stuff. He makes people participate in class, so don't be shy and try raising your hand from time to time.

He has an awesome beard first of all. There were two pop quizzes and two midterms, so the marks were spread out. He is very knowledgeable about greek mythology but his slides have literally nothing on them. You MUST attend class!

He is a great professor. Explains really well. Easy class, his power points only has the topics so class attendance is mandatory in order to get a good mark. He gives you exactly was on the exams and test.
